### Deadline Based Deterministic Forwarding
* **Presentation**: [06)  Deadline Based Deterministic Forwarding](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-detnet-06-deadline-based-deterministic-forwarding-00)
* **Draft**: [draft-ietf-detnet-deadline-based-forwarding](https://datatracker.ietf.org/draft-ietf-detnet-deadline-based-forwarding/)
* **Presented by**: Peng Liu
* **Discussion**:
  * Revision 01 simplifies the document and focuses on two optimal stateless options for scalability: "latency compensation + cycle queueing (CQ)" and "latency compensation + Rotating Priority Queue (RPQ)". Options requiring per-flow state on core nodes have been removed.

