### Timeslot Queueing and Forwarding Mechanism
* **Presentation**: [07) Timeslot Queueing and Forwarding Mechanism](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-detnet-07-timeslot-queueing-and-forwarding-mechanism-00)
* **Draft**: [draft-ietf-detnet-packet-timeslot-mechanism](https://datatracker.ietf.org/draft-ietf-detnet-packet-timeslot-mechanism/)
* **Presented by**: Peng Liu
* **Discussion**:
  * Revision 01 adds operational considerations, moves the evaluations to the appendix, removes PTM detection, and removes the global time slot.
  * Jeong-dong Ryoo asked if the authors had considered merging this draft with Tagged Cyclic Queuing and Forwarding (TCQF) ([draft-ietf-detnet-tcqf](https://datatracker.ietf.org/draft-ietf-detnet-tcqf/)), pointing out that TCQF is class-based while this draft is flow-based. Xiaofu Ji added that there are no technical blockers for a merger, but it depends on the WG's decision.

